{
  "stem": "12462.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the case of the-- IG Farben, the-- we had a charge of aggressive war, which we did not have in the Flick case.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Flick case came first-- the first industrialist case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that charge-- in that case, the leading members of the Flick Concern were charged with using vast numbers of slave laborers, gathered from the west and from the eastern countries, and brought into Germany, and in some cases, treated fairly decently, and other cases, treated very badly.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the one count against the Flick Concern.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second count of the Flick Concern was the taking over of some foreign properties beyond the requirements needed for the-- the maintenance of the occupied Army of Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the rule that-- that an-- under traditional law, you can demand of the occupied country what's required to help you sustain your army that's occupying.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you can't go beyond that in terms of supplying your people back home with riches, or with spoliated goods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The case against IG Farben had not only spoliation and slave labor charges, but the charge of aggressive war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was based largely on the fact that the defendant-- the first defendant in that case, Carl Krauch, K-R-A-U-C-H, [CLEARS THROAT] had been appointed by Goering [CLEARS THROAT] to be the head of the industrialist agencies, almost as if-- it was kind of a super-minister to get war production going.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, he was not a minister, but he had tremendous powers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, he used his own concern.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And while he was in that position of the government, he remained as the-- for some time as the head of the Aufsichtsrat, the supervisory board of the IG Farben Concern.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
